{"tid":2507812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控將斜孭袋丟入城門河 警打撈檢出6支汽油彈 香淑嫻裁定罪成 判監21個月","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:19:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6190768a271e7f480dd21033a373118a0c2054","tid":2507812,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15320&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=5210ff59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15320</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤林(22) #1103沙田<br />\n🛑已還押20天🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：襲擊警務人員 #襲警<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月3日晚上，在沙田瀝源橋近大涌橋路襲擊警員17185。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：在公眾地方管有 #攻擊性武器<br />\n被告被控於同日同地攜有6枚汽油彈。 <br />\n<br />\n📌口頭裁決理由及求情陳詞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14882&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=b5d025b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14882</a><br />\n===============<br />\n📌進一步求情：<br />\n在被告人已經同意的背景報告中可顯示出他與家人的關係親密，家人願意繼續支持及陪伴被告。被告人也已明白控罪嚴重性及願意承擔後果，他希望在服刑完畢後找回職業，支持家人。<br />\n<br />\n律師續指出本案沒有證據指出被告人有意圖使用涉案物品，以及希望法庭考慮到本案是在同一情況發生下，將兩項控罪的刑罰同期執行。<br />\n===============<br />\n📌判刑結果：<br />\n<br />\n控罪1以2個月監禁作為量刑起點<br />\n控罪2以20個月監禁作為量刑起點<br />\n2項控罪的刑期中1個月同期執行<br />\n<br />\n🛑由於被告人經審訊後被定罪，因此沒有刑期扣減，故總刑期為監禁21個月🛑"},{"pid":"e1f49d5a830f9e894e6db04289248bb77de9fa67","tid":2507812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac9ee122058656c1761fd5b30538f225ca7ecf2","tid":2507812,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e5e9fe48d147b2dcb7d0f46bb43564bc9272b2","tid":2507812,"uid":57026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實到依家都唔明<br />\n點樣可以執左個斜孭袋之後證明入面既野就係個位手足的"},{"pid":"884d559e681c0aba3749c5e77509d8571121aa29","tid":2507812,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4e5e9fe48d147b2dcb7d0f46bb43564bc9272b2","tid":2507812,"uid":57026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實到依家都唔明<br />\n點樣可以執左個斜孭袋之後證明入面既野就係個位手足的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"佢對眼就係證據啦，而家香港法庭就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f176abc0d66763207a76109122aaf3c5c44d8b52","tid":2507812,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"送車 寫信 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e66dfde112ca33b717f687e5c6883fd946009f9","tid":2507812,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a4e5e9fe48d147b2dcb7d0f46bb43564bc9272b2","tid":2507812,"uid":57026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實到依家都唔明<br />\n點樣可以執左個斜孭袋之後證明入面既野就係個位手足的"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"🧷 案件爭議點<br />\n 1. PW1 從未見過被告拋任何東西到河面，即使有的話，警察也未有足夠光線去照明。該物件也許是衣服或其他東西。<br />\n 2. 被告從未襲擊 PW1<br />\n 3. 事情實情是PW1 襲擊被告，而PW1 並非在正當執行職務<br />\n 4. 即使被告有襲擊，也只是合法自衛<br />\n 5. PW1 與被告爭執了數分鐘，經拘捕後PW1 才跟PW3 照向河面<br />\n 6. 警員們一直使用電筒照著的東西跟警方所撈起的物件是不同的<br />\n 7. 證物P5 並非水警所撈起的物品<br />\n<br />\n🧷 判斷<br />\n裁判官接納所有控方證人的證供，並裁定被告當日有用頭襲擊警員。被告知道因為自己身上背包有汽油彈，才將背包拋進河中，並進行襲擊行為。<br />\n📋 PW1 及 PW2 是迫不得以要使用武力制服被告，即例如抱起他<br />\n📋 PW1 有足夠光線觀察水中漂浮物<br />\n📋 PW6 撈起的是PW5 所照的漂浮物<br />\n📋 PW7 從 PW6 所檢取的就是PW5 所照的漂浮物"},{"pid":"bc8ffb8bf3ffe050c543a646b0e5bb8b479a1b1c","tid":2507812,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"紅官真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb825d5a20cd312c7300acf658e2c1ae2dd3658","tid":2507812,"uid":61060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4e5e9fe48d147b2dcb7d0f46bb43564bc9272b2","tid":2507812,"uid":57026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實到依家都唔明<br />\n點樣可以執左個斜孭袋之後證明入面既野就係個位手足的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"dead body都dead咗左，仲未明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f131ff54ef9c621af2933c9e580bb6e700c876","tid":2507812,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d22258985a13d6ebd14bbfc55e4c7e239a4f79","tid":2507812,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c77ff6a1cd249ea8c9c52c1329202602efe77d50","tid":2507812,"uid":57026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e66dfde112ca33b717f687e5c6883fd946009f9","tid":2507812,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"p